OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start for most with some
OL,6,Fhill fog and some showery rain in
OL,7,Fplaces. However, cloud gradually
OL,8,Flifting and breaking later to give a
OL,9,Ffew brighter spells. Mostly dry,
OL,10,Falthough isolated light showers
OL,11,Flikely. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FVariable cloud and occasional
OL,14,Fclear spells, with some patchy mist,
OL,15,Ffog or low cloud developing in a few
OL,16,Fplaces. Winds remaining light.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FBright or sunny spells but
OL,19,Fturning cloudier for a time later as
OL,20,Fscattered showers move south, with a
OL,21,Fcooler northerly breeze developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
